promptTemplate:
[TASK] {{taskId}}
action: fix-bug
branch: {{branch}}
files: {{files}}
description: {{description}}
{{#errorMessage}}
Error message:
{{errorMessage}}
{{/errorMessage}}
{{#expectedBehavior}}
Expected behavior:
{{expectedBehavior}}
{{/expectedBehavior}}
---
Fix the bug described above. Run tests to verify the fix.
Work on the specified branch. When done, commit and push the branch (NOT main).
Then use report_task_result with the branch name and commit hash.
